snippet.textDisplay: Excellent video because Dr Seheult cites the medical studies that supports his recommendations.  I am 69 and got COVID-19 in December and it took me 25 days of illness for me to recover at home.  My weaken immune system (due to age) ultimately won the battle so I am looking for ways to help my immune system win the next battle much more quickly.
